lead_paragraph: South African George Coetzee made a flying start to the European Tour's Final Series with a pacesetting seven-under-par 64 at the $7 million Turkish Airlines Open first round in Antalya on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Coetzee Leads Way in Turkey as Willett Opens With 69
